About this item

Smart summary

Generated by AI

The Apple USB-C to Lightning Cable is  1m long  and  compatible with various iPhone, iPad, iPod, and AirPods models . It  connects devices with Lightning connectors to USB-C or Thunderbolt 3 enabled devices  for syncing and charging. The cable  supports fast-charging  on select iPhone and iPad models when used with Apple's 18W, 20W, 29W, 30W, 61W, 87W, or 96W USB-C Power Adapter, making it a versatile charging solution for Apple devices.

About this item

Product details

Connect your device with Lightning connector to your USB-C or Thunderbolt 3 (USB-C) enabled device for syncing and charging, or to your USB-C enabled iPad for charging.

You can also use this cable with your Apple 18W, 20W, 29W, 30W, 61W, 87W or 96W USB‑C Power Adapter to charge your iOS device and even take advantage of the fast-charging feature on select iPhone and iPad models.
